      "content": "thanks for the advice. but i'm also feeling a bit of a headache and my vision is kind of blurry too... i'm worried that if i don't get the insulin right, it's gonna spike even higher later. wouldn't it be safer to just take a small corrective dose now so i dont end up in a huge spike later tonight? i just want to be sure i'm stable.",
